Responsibilities
Your new position includes the following tasks:Receives and initiates the processing of orders and communicates with the customer on finalized pricing,status, lead times, due dates, routings and delivery informationCoordinate customer communication with service team relating to the scheduling of service work and addresing any warranty, replacement and additional parts required needsAddress any and all customer concerns relating to final order shipment status, follow up documentation and preliminary response pertaining to invoicing concerns Requirements:25 – 30 years oldBachelor degreeProficiency in computers (PC,MS Office,CAD) requiredPreferable several years of professional experience in the food or beverage industry is advantagePosses a strong service-mind with excellent customer contact skillsWillingness to travel  extensively within Indonesia and abroadVery good command of verbal and written EnglishAble speak Germany is advantage.
